        SENSORS --> LOGS["🌐 GET /{vmIp}/logs"]
        LOGS --> UPDATE["🖥️ GUI 갱신"]
        UPDATE --> INTERVAL
        
        DISCONNECT["DISCONNECT 버튼 클릭"] --> STOP_POLL["폴링 중지"]
    end
    
    subgraph "🖥️ GUI에 표시되는 내용"
        STATUS -->|status 데이터| HEADER_STATUS["헤더: SYSTEM CONNECTED<br/>LINK SETTINGS: IP, PORT"]
        SENSORS -->|센서 데이터| TELEMETRY["TELEMETRY FEED 테이블<br/>UAM1/altitude: 150<br/>UAM1/speed: 25"]
        LOGS -->|로그 배열| CONSOLE["SYSTEM CONSOLE<br/>[UAM1] Taking off<br/>[UAM1] Ascending"]
    end
```

